description:
a random prompt generator, very simple and friendly for beginners, beautifully colored and organized, and with the possibility of modifying the texts for the random prompts,
To do this, just add more lines of words to the purple nodes.
Works for SDXL and 1.5
name: Simple Random PROMPT Generator
